x4freetext: Charged photoparticle  spectra  from  natural lithium
have  been  measured  using  a  solid-state  counter
telescope,  and  the bremsstrahlung beam of a 32 MeV
The 7Li(g,t)4He cross section shows a great  deal  of
structure  corresponding  to excitation of levels in
the region of the giant resonance.
Also the proton spectrum exhibits a complex structure
